    "Institutional stakeholders, including hospital administrators and insurers, are likely to promote adoption, with policy changes anticipated (Adams et al., 2025).",
    "While AI can support collaboration, it cannot replace the interpersonal decision-making and human nuance essential to team-based care.",
    "Counseling is a core responsibility of SLPs, addressing not only communication but also the emotional and behavioral dimensions of care.",
    "While AI tools such as chatbots and sentiment analysis systems do provide psychoeducational support and monitor well-being, they currently lack the empathy and context sensitivity essential for therapeutic counseling (Bloch-Atefi, 2025).",
    "Despite these limitations, AI chatbots are already in use, and their social interaction capabilities are steadily improving (Haque & Rubya, 2023; Duvenaud, 2025)."
